webpackJsonp([0x60a0096f50fa],{4908:function(e,n){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Fasching, the night before",date:"18 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-18-fasching-the-night-before/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/papascott/394403325/" title="Photo Sharing"><img src="https://farm1.static.flickr.com/186/394403325_79ac1fce4b.jpg" width="500" height="375" alt="IMG 1904" /></a></p>\n<p>Tomorrow Christopher\'s school is celebrating <a href="http://german.about.com/library/weekly/aa020501a.htm"><em>Fasching</em></a>... here are the main components of his costume. Aficionados of 20th century German children\'s literature can probably guess what will come of it.</p>\n<p>Here in northern Germany <em>Fasching</em> or <em>Karneval</em> is strictly for children, unlike in lesser developed parts of the country (although some towns near us celebrate <a href="http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Faslam"><em>Faslam</em></a>, which seems to be <em>Karneval</em> reduced to the bare essentials: getting drunk in a clown costume).</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Soundtrack of Life",date:"16 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-16-soundtrack-of-life/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Hanging Out With The Goats",date:"18 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-18-hanging-out-with-the-goats/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Soundtrack of Life",date:"16 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-16-soundtrack-of-life/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>I don\'t follow every meme that comes along, but the <a href="http://www.lostfocus.de/archives/2007/02/16/soundtrack-of-life/">Soundtrack of Life</a> that\'s going through our company seemed interesting, especially since I never listen to music at random. Here are the rules:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Open your player player (iTunes, Winamp, Media Player, iPod etc.).</li>\n<li>Set it to "Shuffle/Random".</li>\n<li>Press "Play".</li>\n<li>For each answer write the song title that\'s being played.</li>\n<li>For each new question hit the "Next" button.</li>\n<li>Don\'t lie or pretend to be cool - just type the titles.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The result are some titles that I don\'t even recognize...</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Opening Credits:<br />\nNot Like This - Al Jarreau  </li>\n<li>Awakening:<br />\nLucky Star - Madonna<br />\n<em>Not a bad start</em>  </li>\n<li>First Day of School:<br />\nInsincere Because I - The Dandy Warhols  </li>\n<li>Falling in Love:<br />\nSentimental - Kenny G<br />\n<em>The Kenny G CDs are not mine!</em>  </li>\n<li>The First Time:<br />\nNothing Really Matters - Madonna<br />\n<em>In the long run, no</em>  </li>\n<li>Battle Song:<br />\nLeave My Monkey Alone - Warren Zevon<br />\n<em>Or he\'ll bite you!</em></li>\n<li>Breaking Up:<br />\nKuba - Fettes Brot  </li>\n<li>Prom:<br />\nI Want You To Hurt Like I Do - Randy Newman<br />\n<em>Did I ever tell the story of how I missed MamaMaus\' senior prom because of a car accident?</em></li>\n<li>Life:<br />\nBonny &amp; Clyde - Die Toten Hosen<br />\n<em>A life of crime?</em></li>\n<li>Nervous Breakdown:<br />\nPlease - The Nylons  </li>\n<li>Driving:<br />\nThis Fire - Franz Ferdninand  </li>\n<li>Flashback:<br />\nNebraska - Bruce Spingsteen<br />\n<em>Looking back on a life of crime?</em></li>\n<li>Wedding:<br />\nVermissen Baby - Die Ärzte<br />\n<em>Over before it begins</em></li>\n<li>First Born Child:<br />\nLove Is The New Feel Awful - The Dandy Warhols  </li>\n<li>Final Struggle:<br />\nStreets of Fire - Bruce Springsteen  </li>\n<li>Death Scene:<br />\nEr Gehörte Mal Mir - Annett Louisan  </li>\n<li>Funeral:<br />\nNur Geträumt - Nena<br />\n<em>Excellent!</em>  </li>\n<li>Credits:<br />\nTake Me To The River - Talking Heads<br />\n<em>More excellent!</em></li>\n</ul>'},next:{fields:{title:"Wrestlers and Comedians",date:"15 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-15-wrestlers-and-comedians/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Fasching, the night before",date:"18 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-18-fasching-the-night-before/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Wrestlers and Comedians",date:"15 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-15-wrestlers-and-comedians/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>I guess if my home state of Minnesota can elect a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesse_Ventura">professional wrestler as governor</a> there\'s no reason they can\'t elect a comedian to the US Senate: <a href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6364345.stm">BBC: Comedian Franken makes Senate bid</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Anti-Family Policy",date:"15 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-15-anti-family-policy/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Soundtrack of Life",date:"16 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-16-soundtrack-of-life/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:154,pageCount:1101}}}});
